The animator inside me is twitching when I think of the different loading screen reveals. You know the sort of thing - instead of displaying the screen in thirds line-by-line before adding the colours, the screen would load with different bits of it revealing itself in various patterns. Couldn't find a good example on YouTube, so now pondering doing a batch jobby extracting videos of reveals automatically. Examples off the top of my head would be Killed Until Dead, 720 Degrees, Leaderboard...<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.ysrnry.co.uk/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">NickH</a> — Sat Jul 30, 2011 8:56 pm — Replies 7 — Views 910</p><hr />
